dct_title_s: Map of the south point division of Sea Isle City
dct_description_sm: Map of the South Point Division of Sea Isle City, NJ showing Holly Avenue to the North, Inlet Avenue to the south, the Atlantic Ocean to the east and Thoroughfare to the west. Includes an engineer's report of Sea Isle City, Ludlam Island, NJ.
